{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"da7148a721","title":"上海市出版局关于右派分子著译处理问题的回函","origin":"根据文件翻印件打印。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"ba600604db","index":0,"year":1957,"month":12,"day":18,"articleId":"da7148a721"}],"tags":[{"id":"7aac50a8c5","name":"文艺战线","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"7c117e6295","type":"title","text":"上海市出版局关于右派分子著译处理问题的回函","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"da7148a721"},{"id":"0e549252a5","type":"appellation","text":"新文艺出版社：","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"da7148a721"},{"id":"320485ecb5","type":"paragraph","text":"12月1日来函收悉。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"da7148a721"},{"id":"71098af760","type":"paragraph","text":"关于右派分子著译处理问题：","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"da7148a721"},{"id":"1b1fb9c94b","type":"paragraph","text":"一、凡已见报的右派分子著译，请依据我局内发字第50号通知处理；","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"da7148a721"},{"id":"2528b49814","type":"paragraph","text":"二、关于你社内部揭发出来未见报的右派分子著译，为照顾实际影响，未发排的物件，一律暂不发排。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"da7148a721"},{"id":"a26179eee0","type":"paragraph","text":"三、至于一些虽未见报，但有关单位正在对其进行斗争的右派分子著译稿件是否出版问题，请与各单位联系，示具体情况研宄决定。应注意不影响各单位斗争的进行。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"da7148a721"},{"id":"71c9601130","type":"paragraph","text":" 上海市出版局（章）1957年12月18日","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"da7148a721"},{"id":"78ce154c7f","type":"paragraph","text":"抄送：中共上海市委宣传部","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"da7148a721"},{"id":"874f1e098c","type":"paragraph","text":"中共上海市委宣传部收文","index":9,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"da7148a721"},{"id":"14a45e1cf0","type":"paragraph","text":"编号：2567","index":10,"publication